-- Leighton Limits Hochtief Board's Access to Information, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   O l i v e r   S u e s s
-- 2010-10-12T05:20:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/leighton-limits-hochtief-board-s-access-to-information-handelsblatt-says.html
Hochtief AG ’s subsidiary Leighton
Holding Ltd. is limiting information for supervisory board
members from the Essen, Germany-based builder,  Handelsblatt 
reported, citing the Australian company.  An unidentified spokesman for Hochtief, which is the target
of a takeover offer by Spain’s largest builder, said Leighton’s
move would be “normal legal procedure,” the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
